[
  {
    "startTime": 0.067,
    "endTime": 4.05,
    "text": "Now I thought I'd share some of my favorite #myweirdroommate stories from you guys."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 4.103,
    "endTime": 5.137,
    "text": "Here we go."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 5.137,
    "endTime": 7.439,
    "text": "This first one is from @chrislilli."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 7.44,
    "endTime": 9.75,
    "text": "He says, \"I used to live with a guy who would put ketchup straight onto our glass coffee table to dip french fries in so he could avoid cleaning a dish.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 15.81,
    "endTime": 17.584,
    "text": "[ Audience groans ]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 17.584,
    "endTime": 19.45,
    "text": "[ Laughs ]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 19.45,
    "endTime": 20.919999999999998,
    "text": "Wow."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 20.92,
    "endTime": 23.289,
    "text": "This one is from @MelLynn."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 23.289,
    "endTime": 29.024,
    "text": "She says, \"My roommate used to knock on my bedroom door in the middle of the night and when I opened it, she would say, 'Just checking'.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 29.194,
    "endTime": 30.83,
    "text": "[ Laughter and applause ]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 30.83,
    "endTime": 33.699,
    "text": "Okay. Just terrified."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 33.7,
    "endTime": 35.235,
    "text": "Okay."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 35.235,
    "endTime": 39.972,
    "text": "This one is from @wyyyyyit."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 39.972,
    "endTime": 41.474000000000004,
    "text": "How many Y's?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 41.474,
    "endTime": 42.940999999999995,
    "text": "I think it's five Y's."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 42.942,
    "endTime": 45.945,
    "text": "W-h-- -W-y-y-y-y-y-i-t."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 45.945,
    "endTime": 47.446,
    "text": "-Wyyyyit. -Wyyyyit."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 47.446,
    "endTime": 54.614,
    "text": "She says, \"I wanted to get out of my apartment ASAP. I saw an ad that said,'Looking for a clean, quiet roommate.' I called the number. It was my roommate.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 54.82,
    "endTime": 57.189,
    "text": "[ Audience oohs ]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 57.189,
    "endTime": 58.758,
    "text": "Do you like piña coladas?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 58.758,
    "endTime": 60.459,
    "text": "[ Chuckles ]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 60.459,
    "endTime": 62.528000000000006,
    "text": "This next one's from @mahuls."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 62.528,
    "endTime": 63.73,
    "text": "-Oh. Mahuls. -She said --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 63.73,
    "endTime": 64.831,
    "text": "You know Mahuls?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 64.831,
    "endTime": 66.265,
    "text": "Oh, Mahuls. I love Mahuls."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 66.266,
    "endTime": 68.101,
    "text": "[ Laughter ]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 68.101,
    "endTime": 69.768,
    "text": "No, that's not the non-alcoholic beverage that you drink."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 70.268,
    "endTime": 70.903,
    "text": "Oh, it's not?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 70.903,
    "endTime": 72.304,
    "text": "-That is O'Doul's. -Oh, that's O'Doul's."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 72.304,
    "endTime": 73.806,
    "text": "It's okay. I'm sorry. I love O'Doul's."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 74.206,
    "endTime": 76.94200000000001,
    "text": "Mahuls is a non-alcoholic bar."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 77.342,
    "endTime": 81.213,
    "text": "-Non-alcoholic. [ Laughs ] -The whole bar, non-alcoholic."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 81.913,
    "endTime": 84.75,
    "text": "That's actually a play land. It's a Gymboree."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 84.75,
    "endTime": 86.452,
    "text": "-It's a Gymboree. -Gymboree for children."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 86.452,
    "endTime": 88.12,
    "text": "Yeah, it's not even for adults. It's for children."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 88.12,
    "endTime": 89.12100000000001,
    "text": "The ball pit."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 89.121,
    "endTime": 90.19,
    "text": "It's a trampoline park."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 90.19,
    "endTime": 91.324,
    "text": "-Yeah. -I don't want to get into it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 91.324,
    "endTime": 92.458,
    "text": "Lot of lawsuits."
