    "text": "-...That's the problem. -[ Laughing ] Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 121.687,
    "endTime": 122.655,
    "text": "That's why I can't sleep at night."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 123.655,
    "endTime": 125.425,
    "text": "I can't see most of my tattoos."
  },
