    "startTime": 136.302,
    "endTime": 137.602,
    "text": "-I forgot. -I don't have a reflection."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 137.603,
    "endTime": 139.405,
    "text": "- You don't understand what -- -You're Count Dracula Jr."
  },
