  {
    "startTime": 156.355,
    "endTime": 158.19,
    "text": "Oh. [ Laughter ]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 158.19,
    "endTime": 159.792,
    "text": "She says, \"My roommate would number her Kraft singles with a Sharpie so she'd know if we took one.\""
